Bushveld Minerals has provided an updated Mineral Resources and Ore Reserves for the Vametco vanadium mine. The resources and reserve estimation was carried out by MSA Group Inc in accordance with the terminology and definitions given in the JORC Code (2012). Fortune Mojapelo, CEO of Bushveld Minerals Limited, commented: “It is pleasing to see this orebody continue to deliver consistently, as per the reserves and resources estimates it is based upon. This gives us the confidence to pursue further growth in the years ahead, knowing that we have decades of mine life in front of us. It is updates like this that remind us what a unique and world-class asset we possess and that we must ensure it gets developed to its full potential over time.” Key highlights